Bitnami Helm charts assume the following prerequisites:

* A Kubernetes v1.12+ cluster running. Check out these [Get Started guides](/<%= platform_path %>) to setup a Kubernetes environment with ease.
* The [*kubectl command line (kubectl CLI)*](/<%= platform_path %>/faq/get-started/install-kubectl) installed.
* The [Helm v3.x](/<%= platform_path %>/faq/get-started/install-configure-helm) CLI installed.

Some Helm charts also require a PersistentVolume storage provider and one or more ReadWriteMany volumes.
